rows.field_323784: A brand asset management solution that enables businesses to manage digital brand assets and resources, such as logos, fonts, styles, write-ups and other media.

It's important for designers, content creators, and marketing experts to make sure their work stays consistent in order to keep their brand's image as professional as possible. As a business expands, its brand assets also expand. It is not unthinkable for a business to amass hundreds of digital marketing resources in such a short period of time. This template provides an immediate solution to this dilemma.

This template helps to build a brand asset management database, which can help a business keep track of all of its digital brand assets or resources, like logos, fonts, and so on. With this template, managing brand assets becomes straightforward and organized.

This template helps to build a brand asset management database that can help a business keep track of all of its digital brand assets or resources. In total, it only keeps track of six tables. These are Logos, Styles, Graphics, Audio and videos, Marketing write-ups, and Creators. 

To use this template, start by filling in the Creators table with the basic contact information for every service provider that the business has worked with in the past. The information in this table will be linked to records found in the other tables. When that's done, just keep recording and uploading every branding resource or asset that the business has at its disposal.

Create or explore the predefined table views to make it easy and efficient to organize all your digital branding resources.
